\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mfb1665702637602.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mfb1665702637602.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mfb1665702637602.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mfb1665702637602\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines where the sort order of the list view can be changed. <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default).\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mfb1665702637602__p_d105317e1_d105318e1_d105319e1\">LSortChg<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mfb1665702637602__table_d12446e1_d12447e1_d12448e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mfb1665702637602__table_d12446e1_d12447e1_d12448e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mfb1665702637602__table_d12446e1_d12447e1_d12448e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mfb1665702637602__table_d12446e1_d12447e1_d12448e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mfb1665702637602__table_d12446e1_d12447e1_d12448e1__entry__2\">Sort order of the list view can be changed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mfb1665702637602__table_d12446e1_d12447e1_d12448e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default)</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mfb1665702637602__table_d12446e1_d12447e1_d12448e1__entry__2\">Sort order of the list view cannot be\n                     changed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mfb1665702637602__section_fbm_kvt_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d433614e119\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mfb1665702637602__table_d12449e1_d12450e1_d12451e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Controls whether the  LSortOrder property is read.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mfb1665702637602__section_uz4_vvt_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d433614e167\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mfb1665702637602__p_d105332e1_d105333e1_d105334e1\">This is a static property. It can be set in\n            ProcScript only before the form is displayed, for example in the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">exec</span>\n            operation before the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">display</span> command.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mfb1665702637602__pre_a5j_wvt_ywb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\n $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"LSortChg=True\"\n edit\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mfb1665702637602__p_d105335e1_d105336e1_d105337e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see the \"$properties\" and \"$fieldproperties\" topics.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mfb1665702637602__section_r4x_xvt_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d433614e197\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702634237.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" title=\"The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.\">utree (Tree)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eve1665702637672.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>LSortOrder</a><p>Defines the sort order the first time the column header is clicked. The default is ascending order.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$properties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldproperties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614553\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614553\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "LSortChg Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Determines where the sort order of the list view can be changed. True or False (default). LSortChg = \" True | False \" Value Description True Sort order of the list view can be changed False (default) Sort order of the list view cannot be changed. Usage Dynamic? No Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Controls whether the LSortOrder property is read. Using in ProcScript This is a static property. It can be set in ProcScript only before the form is displayed, for example in the exec operation before the edit or display command. operation exec $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"LSortChg=True\" edit end; exec Copy You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see the \"$properties\" and \"$fieldproperties\" topics. Applies To utree (Tree) Related Links LSortOrder Defines the sort order the first time the column header is clicked. The default is ascending order. $properties Return or set the current widget properties of a field. $fieldproperties Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}